CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 14, 1953, pg. 3 reads: "Chest Drive Unit Leaders - Mrs. Doris Finch and Albert J. Charles are two of the neighborhood unit leaders in current Community Chest Drive. Headquarters for their neighborhood unit is the Centre Avenue YMCA.  The drive closes Nov. 19. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Community Chest drive leaders Doris Finch and Albert J. Charles, standing behind table in front of Henry O. Tanner, "Christ and His Mother," Centre Avenue YMCA
